{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"637a64a046","title":"毛泽东关于到河南遂平调查人民公社问题给陈伯达的信","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a7e4b08869","index":0,"year":1958,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"637a64a046"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4b9cb1cabd","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于到河南遂平调查人民公社问题给陈伯达的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"270593ca75","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"d1fb99cf25","type":"appellation","text":"伯达同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"bba926bbe1","type":"paragraph","text":"想了一下，你和张春桥同志似以早三天去河南卫星公社进行调查工作为适宜，不必听廿一日刘子厚同志的报告。集中精力在卫星公社调查七天至十天，为杭州会议准备意见，很有必要。可带李友九去帮忙。如同意，请告叶子龙同志，为你们调一架专机即飞郑州。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"b030d24708","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十月十九日上午七时","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"69ec438c94","type":"paragraph","text":"到郑州时，最好能请史向生同志和你们一道去卫星社。史对人民公社有研究，他去过卫星社。他是省委书记。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"d8e9132d37","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"286acf0f95","type":"appellation","text":"伯达同志：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"591980f9b8","type":"paragraph","text":"去河南时，请把《马、恩、列、斯论共产主义社会》一书带几本去，你们调查团几个人，每人一本，边调查，边读书，白天调查，晚上阅读，有十几天，也就可以读完了。建议将胡绳、李友九都带去，练习去向劳动人民做调查工作的方法和态度，善于看问题和提问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"1b4e5f2dc5","type":"paragraph","text":"我过了下星期就去郑州，一到，即可听你们关于卫星社观察所得的报告，在四省第一书记会议上予以讨论。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"4f45182621","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十月十九日上午七时半","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"4701cd2d2c","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"5d0bff5ac6","type":"appellation","text":"陈伯达同志：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"cd9cf935f8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们调查研究卫星社大约要一个星期，包括调查团(社)营(大队)连(队)的各项问题。然后，请找遂平县级同志们座谈几次，研究全县各项问题。以上请酌量处理。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"6358a8e5e2","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十月廿三日下午五时","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"d5577d07e5","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"b7dce299d8","type":"appellation","text":"陈伯达同志：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"91e64cb234","type":"paragraph","text":"回信收到。我还须几天才能出发。如果遂平调查已毕，你们可去附近某一个县再作几天调查，以资比较。于十一月二号或三号回到郑州即可。已令吴冷西、田家英二同志昨日夜车出发，分赴修武七里营两处调查几天再去郑州。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"},{"id":"8af615f18a","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十月二十八日上午四时","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046"}],"page":{"id":"9af03a6567","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"637a64a046","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}